OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and wet start to the
OL,6,Fday, with rain gradually clearing
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. Turning brighter,
OL,8,Fwith plenty of sunny spells developing
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. Perhaps an
OL,10,Fisolated shower remains possible.
OL,11,FFeeling warmer than of late, but
OL,12,Frather breezy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FStaying mostly dry through
OL,15,Fthe evening and overnight, with plenty
OL,16,Fof clear spells. The cloudiest skies
OL,17,Ftowards the north, where the odd light
OL,18,Fshower is still possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
