OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRather cloudy with some
OL,6,Fsunny spells, these developing more
OL,7,Fwidely later in the afternoon. Showers
OL,8,Fare also possible, especially across
OL,9,Fthe Lake District. A chilly
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA fine
OL,13,Ffew days on Sunday and Monday, with
OL,14,Fplenty of warm spells of sunshine and
OL,15,Flight winds. Increasing chance of
OL,16,Fshowery rain moving in through the day
OL,17,Fon Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
